title: 10 Best Windows Utilities From Nirsoft
tags: 15 NirSoft Utilities Every Windows User Should Have
description: Nirsoft has made some of the best apps for Windows and in this video, we have picked our top 10 utilities from Nirsoft.   Download Nirlaucher from here --     [List of Apps used in the video]   #1 ProduKey -- find the product key   #2 CurrPorts   #3 ChromeCacheView -- See Images Store in the Browser Cache    #4 VideoCacheView -- Find Videos Store in the Browser Cache    #5 HostedNetworkStarter -- Create WiFi hotspot   #6 QuickSetDNS -- Change DNS server with one click   #7 FolderChangesView   #8 Wireless Key Viewer -- find all the saved WiFi password   #9 WebBrowserPassView --  Recover password saved in browser.    #10 Wireless Network watcher -- find the devices on your network    I use Audio from YouTube audio library.
